# `__PACKAGE_NAME__`

Effect service package with explicit contract, live, and deterministic test
boundaries. Import contracts from `/schemas`, `/errors`, and `/service`; compose
production through `/live`; tests may use `/test` and narrow `/testing/*` paths.

The package owns its semantic schemas and service contract. It does not own app
runtime execution, transport adapters, or provider runbooks. Update the nearest
repository architecture owner when a public schema or service operation changes;
update its proof/critical-journey owner when observable behavior changes. No
operational runbook is required until this package acquires an external system or
consequential operation.
